## ! and ? ## {#wording-interrobang}

Insert into 5.10 Identifiers [**lex.name**]

: *identifier*
:: *identifier-nondigit*
:: *identifier* *identifier-nondigit*
:: *identifier* *digit*
: <ins>*identifier-special*:</ins>
:: <ins>*identifier* *identifier-special-char*</ins>
: <ins>*identifier-special-char*: one of</ins>
:: <ins>**!** **?**</ins>

